---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components"

import Link from "@components/utilities/Link.astro"
import LinkSecondary from "@components/utilities/LinkSecondary.astro"

import { siteInfo } from "@constant/site-info"
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div
    class="blue-950 absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 via-blue-700 to-blue-950"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute h-20 w-20 animate-ping rounded-full bg-white/10"
      style="top: 15%; left: 10%; animation-duration: 8s; animation-delay: 0.5s;"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="absolute h-12 w-12 animate-ping rounded-full bg-white/10"
      style="top: 40%; left: 25%; animation-duration: 6s; animation-delay: 1s;"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="absolute h-16 w-16 animate-ping rounded-full bg-white/10"
      style="top: 20%; right: 20%; animation-duration: 7s; animation-delay: 2s;"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="absolute h-10 w-10 animate-ping rounded-full bg-white/10"
      style="top: 50%; right: 10%; animation-duration: 5s; animation-delay: 0s;"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="absolute h-14 w-14 animate-ping rounded-full bg-white/10"
      style="bottom: 30%; left: 15%; animation-duration: 9s; animation-delay: 1.5s;"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 left-0 h-24 opacity-20">
    <svg
      viewBox="0 0 1200 120"
      preserveAspectRatio="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <path
        d="M0,0V46.29c47.79,22.2,103.59,32.17,158,28,70.36-5.37,136.33-33.31,206.8-37.5C438.64,32.43,512.34,53.67,583,72.05c69.27,18,138.3,24.88,209.4,13.08,36.15-6,69.85-17.84,104.45-29.34C989.49,25,1113-14.29,1200,52.47V0Z"
        opacity=".25"
        class="animate-wave-left fill-blue-50"
      ></path>
      <path
        d="M0,0V15.81C13,36.92,27.64,56.86,47.69,72.05,99.41,111.27,165,111,224.58,91.58c31.15-10.15,60.09-26.07,89.67-39.8,40.92-19,84.73-46,130.83-49.67,36.26-2.85,70.9,9.42,98.6,31.56,31.77,25.39,62.32,62,103.63,73,40.44,10.79,81.35-6.69,119.13-24.28s75.16-39,116.92-43.05c59.73-5.85,113.28,22.88,168.9,38.84,30.2,8.66,59,6.17,87.09-7.5,22.43-10.89,48-26.93,60.65-49.24V0Z"
        opacity=".5"
        class="animate-wave-right fill-blue-50"
      ></path>
      <path
        d="M0,0V5.63C149.93,59,314.09,71.32,475.83,42.57c43-7.64,84.23-20.12,127.61-26.46,59-8.63,112.48,12.24,165.56,35.4C827.93,77.22,886,95.24,951.2,90c86.53-7,172.46-45.71,248.8-84.81V0Z"
        class="animate-wave-center fill-blue-50"
      ></path>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden opacity-10">
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 h-96 w-96 rounded-full border-2 border-white/30"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/3 h-64 w-64 rounded-full border border-white/20"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute right-1/4 bottom-1/4 h-80 w-80 rounded-full border-2 border-white/30"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="absolute grid h-full w-full grid-cols-12 gap-4 opacity-10">
      <div class="col-span-1 bg-white/10"></div>
      <div class="col-span-2 bg-white/5"></div>
      <div class="col-span-1 bg-white/10"></div>
      <div class="col-span-3 bg-white/5"></div>
      <div class="col-span-1 bg-white/10"></div>
      <div class="col-span-2 bg-white/5"></div>
      <div class="col-span-2 bg-white/10"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="text-white">
        <div
          class="hero-title mb-6 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-blue-600/30 px-4 py-2 backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
          <div class="mr-2 h-3 w-3 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-green-400">
          </div>

          <span class="text-sm font-medium"
            >Estamos en línea y listos para ayudarte</span
          >
        </div>

        <h1 class="hero-title mb-6 text-4xl font-bold md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          Conecta con <span class="text-ibwt-secondary">iBluewave</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-paragraph mb-8 text-xl text-gray-300">
          Estamos aquí para responder a tus preguntas y ayudarte a explorar las
          profundidades con nuestra tecnología submarina innovadora.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <Link
            href="#formulario"
            className="bg-ibwt-secondary hero-btn-primary inline-flex items-center rounded-md px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white transition-colors"
          >
            <Icon
              name="basic-icons/email"
              size={25}
              class="mr-2"
            />
            Enviar Mensaje
          </Link>

          <LinkSecondary
            href="#mapa"
            className="hero-btn-secondary inline-flex items-center rounded-md px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white"
          >
            <Icon
              name="basic-icons/pin"
              size={25}
              class="mr-2"
            />
            Visítanos
          </LinkSecondary>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div
          class="hero-title relative rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400/20 to-blue-600/20 p-8 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
          <div class="mb-6 flex items-center">
            <div class="mr-2 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-400"></div>
            <div class="bg-ibwt-secondary mr-2 h-3 w-3 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="mr-2 h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></div>
            <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-white/20"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-white">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div
                class="mr-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-600/30"
              >
                <Icon
                  name="basic-icons/phone"
                  size={25}
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-medium">Línea Directa</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300">{siteInfo.phone}</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div
                class="mr-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-600/30"
              >
                <Icon
                  name="basic-icons/email"
                  size={25}
                />
              </div>

              <div>
                <h3 class="font-medium">Correo Electrónico</h3>
                <a
                  href={`mailto:${siteInfo.email}`}
                  class="text-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white hover:underline"
                  >{siteInfo.email}</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div
                class="mr-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-600/30"
              >
                <Icon
                  name="basic-icons/pin"
                  size={25}
                />
              </div>

              <div>
                <h3 class="font-medium">Ubicación</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300">Barranquilla, Atlántico</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">
                <span>Respuesta en menos de</span>
                <span class="block font-medium text-white">24 horas</span>
              </div>

              <Link
                href="#formulario"
                className="bg-ibwt-secondary px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white"
              >
                Contactar Ahora
              </Link>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-ibwt-primary/30 absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 h-12 w-12 rotate-12 rounded-lg"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-ibwt-secondary/50 absolute -top-6 -right-6 h-16 w-16 rounded-full"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 left-0">
    <svg
      viewBox="0 0 1200 120"
      preserveAspectRatio="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      class="h-16 w-full"
    >
      <path
        d="M0,0V46.29c47.79,22.2,103.59,32.17,158,28,70.36-5.37,136.33-33.31,206.8-37.5C438.64,32.43,512.34,53.67,583,72.05c69.27,18,138.3,24.88,209.4,13.08,36.15-6,69.85-17.84,104.45-29.34C989.49,25,1113-14.29,1200,52.47V120H0Z"
        class="fill-white"
      ></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
